{"tid":2166950,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"吾城學生會係咪會執柒？","createTime":"2020-08-20T18:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T04:32:58.000Z","uid":30836,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7d1f078ceb405d8366385884507cdcb2c269e2","tid":2166950,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"有幾多人真係會主動交錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位同學：<br />\n<br />\n【2020/21 學年學生會會費收取安排】<br />\n<br />\n學生會於 8 月 17 日公佈會費新繳交安排後，收到了不少同學就繳費方法以及是否遭大學校方打壓等的查詢，故特此作出聲明交代。<br />\n<br />\n本年度會費收取安排改動十分倉促。多年來，大學財務處均為學生會財務行政提供協助，本會會費亦一向由財務處代收（與學費一併收取）。然而，大學財務處卻突然於本年度六月起，以審計問題為由，單方面拒絕再為本會代收會費。換言之，學生會被逼自行收取會費，亦未能經財務處得知會員是否已繳交會費。校方突然宣佈此重大改動，無可厚非為學生會行政帶來繁重的負擔。<br />\n<br />\n由校方表態起，學生會於兩個多月間多次與校方進行協商，反映學生會倉猝間須自行收取會費的難處，無奈大學仍然執意拒絕代收。學生會亦曾提出參考其它大學的做法「分拆帳單」，由同學於繳交學費時自行選擇是否繳交會費，然而亦遭到校方反對，同時校方亦拒絕設立過渡期予學生會時間準備自行收費。<br />\n<br />\n香港其他大專院校均有大學校方代學生會收取會費的做法，多次追問下校方依舊沒有交代何來只有城大會出現「審計問題」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，學生會於宣佈會費收取安排翌日由大學財務處代發電郵全體本科生，但校方卻不願將介紹會費收取安排之網站（<a href=\"http://payment.cityusu.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpayment.cityusu.hk&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5R9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9e292d0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">payment.cityusu.hk</a>）列於電郵內容中。<br />\n<br />\n司馬昭之心路人皆知，本會在此譴責校方以行政為名打壓學生會之舉。<br />\n<br />\n為準備自行處理會費收取，學生會上下已加派人手協調工作，有不便之處還望同學見諒。本會亦將於不日內再向同學說明本會福利及財政開支。<br />\n<br />\n在此我謹代表學生會感謝同學一路以來的鼓勵及鞭策，本會必盡力而為，無懼打壓，堅守學生會的本份和責任。<br />\n<br />\n香港城市大學學生會<br />\n署理會長　黃盛恒　上<br />\n2020 年 8 月 19 日<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/cityusu/12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcityusu%2F12&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5R9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=89f1e24f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cityusu/12</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你 TG條俾錢Link都貼唔好：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://payment.cityusu.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpayment.cityusu.hk&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5R9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=e65c0a6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://payment.cityusu.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/143630_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F143630_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=89c12a35&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"3b21b53039e6cffadd52f8b08074b3f8f8681ad0","tid":2166950,"uid":30836,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ShabbyHugeHawk-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FShabbyHugeHawk-size_restricted.gif&h=86976b3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdcd1c73b5caa97ae759afe1d60111b22ed2712d","tid":2166950,"uid":30836,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpT5t7p.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpT5t7p.gif&h=c4a2047a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b350e2a57fc04f29ccce1d9698a6cda8a56369b","tid":2166950,"uid":199845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:31:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f6a322e6dbf9dedc5c22b18cf7ad361f6b439bb4","tid":2166950,"uid":366724,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"唔交=港豬<br />\n淨係依一年城大編委做嘅嘢已經值晒<br />\n影到咁多黑警黑材料<br />\n今年仲要比城大「針對」<br />\n唔支持仲想玩學生會活動、攞着數？<br />\nJust dream it <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Shitty boy"},{"pid":"910fee01d1ea9230ac077cd762b4d5a29aae4d98","tid":2166950,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6a322e6dbf9dedc5c22b